FBIS3-54979 "drsov003_r_94003" FBIS-SOV-94-003 Document Type:Daily Report 5 Jan 1994 Azerbaijan `Fierce Battles' Continue LD0501115894 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network in Russian 0600 GMT 5 Jan 94 LD0501115894 Moscow Ostankino Television First Channel Network Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [From the "Novosti" newscast] [Text] Fierce battles are continuing in Nagorno-Karabakh between Azerbaijani formations and NKR [Nagorno-Karabakh Republic] forces. After intensive shelling, Azerbaijani troops have begun an offensive along the whole frontline from the Iraqi border [as heard] down to the Mrav Ridge [Crest] in the north of NKR's Mardakertskiy Rayon. There are casualties and fatalities on both sides. Stepanakert has denied Baku's reports of the Azeri Army's successful capture of a number of settlements in the north section of the Karabakh front.
